      "html": "<p>古英语 <i class=\"foreign notranslate\">feþerbedd</i>； 参见 <a title=\"Etymology, meaning and definition of feather \" class=\"crossreference notranslate\" href=\"/cn/word/feather\">feather</a>（n.）+ <a title=\"Etymology, meaning and definition of bed \" class=\"crossreference notranslate\" href=\"/cn/word/bed\">bed</a>（n.）。</p>"
    },
    {
      "title": "feather-weight<div class=\"pl-2 flex-1 text-textSecondary text-xl font-serif\">(n.)</div>",
      "html": "<p>也称为 <i class=\"foreign notranslate\">featherweight</i>，意为“规则允许的最轻重量”，始于1812年（早期仅称为 <i class=\"foreign notranslate\">feather</i>，始于1760年），源自 <a title=\"Etymology, meaning and definition of feather \" class=\"crossreference notranslate\" href=\"/cn/word/feather\">feather</a>（n.）和 <a title=\"Etymology, meaning and definition of weight \" class=\"crossreference notranslate\" href=\"/cn/word/weight\">weight</a>（n.）。最初用于马术比赛； 拳击中作为特定重量级别的使用始于1889年。</p>"
    }
  ]
